<footer class="contact" id="contacto">
  <div class="contact-content">
    <h2>Trabajemos juntos</h2>
    <p>¿Tenés un proyecto que necesite voz? Escribime.</p>
    <div class="contact-links">
      <a href="https://instagram.com/santi.dora" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="contact-link">
        Instagram
      </a>
      <a href="https://facebook.com/santi.dora" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="contact-link">
        Facebook
      </a>
      <a href="https://doblaje.fandom.com/es/wiki/Santiago_Dora" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="contact-link">
        Doblaje Wiki
      </a>
    </div>
    <p class="contact-location">Córdoba, Argentina</p>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
  .contact {
    padding: 6rem 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
  }
  .contact h2 {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
  }
  .contact > .contact-content > p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin: 0 0 2rem;
  }
  .contact-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .contact-link {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  .contact-link:hover {
    color: var(--color-accent-hover);
  }
  .contact-location {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    opacity: 0.7;
  }
</style>
